headline: Western Digital to Announce Second Quarter Fiscal Year 2026 Financial Results on January 29, 2026
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., January 12, 2026--Western Digital Corp. (Nasdaq: WDC) plans to announce its second quarter fiscal year 2026 financial results after the market closes on Thursday, January 29, 2026. The company will host a conference call with the investment community to discuss these results on January 29, 2026, at 1:30 p.m. Pacific / 4:30 p.m. Eastern. A live audio webcast and a webcast replay of the conference call will be available at investor.wdc.com.
